At Middleton is a 2013 American romantic comedy film directed by Adam Rodgers and starring Andy Garc√≠a , Vera Farmiga , Taissa Farmiga , and Spencer Lofranco .
Written by Glenn German and Adam Rodgers , the film follows a man and a woman as they meet and fall in love while taking their children on a college tour .
The film had its world premiere at the Seattle International Film Festival on May 17 , 2013 .
It was released in a limited release and through video on demand on January 31 , 2014 by Anchor Bay Films .